### Test Dataset Upload
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="ecommerce_sales.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./samples/ecommerce_sales.csv
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Test Get All Datasets
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets

### Test Get Dataset by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}

### Test Get Dataset Profile (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/profile

### Build Metadata Index (required before formula inference auto-run)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/index:build
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"maxColumnsForCorrelation": 10,
	"topKEdgesPerColumn": 5,
	"sampleRows": 5000,
	"includeStringPatterns": true,
	"includeDistributions": true
}

### Run Formula Inference (Auto)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/formula-inference/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"targetColumn": "total",
	"mode": "Auto",
	"options": {
		"maxColumns": 3,
		"maxDepth": 2,
		"epsilonAbs": 0.0001,
		"includePercentageColumns": false
	}
}

### Run Formula Inference (Manual)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/formula-inference/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"targetColumn": "total",
	"mode": "Manual",
	"manualExpression": "unit_price * quantity"
}

### Get Formula Inference Metadata
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/formula-inference

### Finalize Import with Optional Formula Inference Trigger
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/datasets/{{datasetId}}/finalize
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"targetColumn": "total",
	"ignoredColumns": [],
	"columnTypeOverrides": {},
	"currencyCode": "BRL",
	"formulaInference": {
		"enabled": true,
		"maxColumns": 3,
		"maxDepth": 2,
		"epsilonAbs": 0.0001,
		"includePercentageColumns": false
	}
}
